{"tid":84958,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲高爾：係休息！唔係退休！","createTime":"2017-01-18T02:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T17:12:42.000Z","uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a255ef40de94ebedcbaed269e45a2efcc7d8b8","tid":84958,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=SUxq16C8nhGvTWbylUP3LBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=cd62ff31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】玩咩！前曼聯領隊雲高爾澄清退休報道，堅稱自己正在休息而非退休，到7月才有決定。<br />\n<br />\n有戰術大師之稱的前曼聯領隊雲高爾（Louis van Gaal）創下轉軚紀錄，他日前接受荷蘭《電訊報》訪問表示自己無意再執教球隊，令各大媒體爭相報道他退休的消息。不過，他在周二晚接受西班牙《Cadena Ser》電台訪問，卻澄清退休的說法。<br />\n<br />\n「不，不，不，我沒有退休。我僅僅是休息而已，之後我會再決定是否退休。一切都視乎收到的條件而定，7月再定！」原來，今年夏天才是雲高爾的D-Day，還收到西甲球隊的邀約。<br />\n<br />\n「我可能重返西班牙。1個月或5周之前，華倫西亞邀請我擔任教練，當時我回絕了。」雲高爾說。該荷蘭名帥之前還拒絕過中超球隊的盛情，據悉3季酬勞高達4400萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sports.now.com/home/other/details?id=17101130014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fother%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D17101130014&d=SUxq16C8nhGvTWbylUP3LBpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=2ce8f5be\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.now.com/home/other/details?id=17101130014</a><br />\n<br />\n方丈彈出彈入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef8e868b24c0bb84e67fa7e0c58bc8a11d9378b","tid":84958,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:47:57.000Z","msg":"番荷蘭搞搞D荷蘭青訓ok?"},{"pid":"3a08dc332a5f1e36052e96e1fc9cdc7345ab51bf","tid":84958,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T04:52:06.000Z","msg":"雲族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bb69a33012169337b1a7742f115ac65a5bac00","tid":84958,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"下年回家執摩狗D蘇州屎"},{"pid":"349128d30c4cad26a0a